data.description: Great opportunity to own a newer construction home built in 2017 loaded with upgrades!! Spacious open floor plan features luxury vinyl laminate flooring, and kitchen with 42'' cabinets, granite center island, soft close cabinets, glass tile backsplash, walk in pantry, and stainless steel appliances.  Large great room is perfect for entertaining with trey ceilings and nice sized family room.  Master suite offers trey ceilings, spacious walk in closet with built in shelving, and 3 windows for great natural lighting.  French doors from the family room leads to a screened porch with brick pavers overlooking an oversized corner lot on a quiet street.  IMPACT WINDOWS AND DOORS!!  Great location minutes from the Manatee pocket, great restaurants, park, and marinas. BR 3 does not have a closet, but can be easily added.
